<h1>Options</h1>
The Cycle Plugin provides many options for customizing your slideshow.  The default option values can be overridden by
passing an option object to the <code class="inline">cycle</code> method, by using
metadata on the container element, or by redefining the values in your own code.
<p>
For more about options, see the <a href="options.html">Options Reference</a> page.
</p>

